/b> I don’t have an item to donate, but I’d like to make a monetary contribution. Is that okay?\r\n\r\n<b>A:</b> Unfortunately, we are unable to accept monetary donations at this time. CommuniLink is a third party platform dedicated to matching household good donations with those in need. We do not claim ownership of any of the items listed on our site. However, if you find an organization using our tool that sparks your interest, feel free to contact them directly to make a monetary donation!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Q:</b> You keep saying you accept “household goods.” Can you define household goods?\r\n\r\n<b>A:</b> We’d be happy to! We define “household goods” as a tangible item that is used inside the house on an everyday basis. Some examples include dressers, lamps, pots and pans, etc.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Q:</b> I’m an organization acting on behalf of someone in need. What kinds of items can I request?\r\n\r\n<b>A:</b> You may request household goods (see definition above) and clothing. Food pantries may put out requests for food. You may NOT request monetary donations. Any such posts seen will be deleted.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Q:</b> How can I delete my posting?\r\n\r\n<b>A:</b> Directly beneath your post, you’ll see the options to ‘Comment,’ ‘Favorite,’ and ‘Delete.” Click delete.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Q:</b> Does my post expire?\r\n\r\n<b>A:</b> Your post will not expire! However, if you haven’t received a response to a post listed several weeks prior, we encourage you to repost. Activity on the site will push your listing to the bottom and sometimes next page. A new post will ensure visibility.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Q:</b> How often can I post a donation or request an item?\r\n\r\n<b>A:</b> Donations are always welcome! Requests are as well, however we encourage you to share the wealth. J\r\n\r\n<b>Q:</b> Can I post a request anonymously?\r\n\r\n<b>A:</b> We require that organizations identify themselves when registering, so anonymous requests are prohibited.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Q:</b> Can I list a donation anonymously?\r\n\r\n<b>A:</b> Yes! When you register as a donor, you aren’t required to provide a name. Just make your username “Anonymous.”\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nStill have a question we haven’t touched upon? Email us! <a href=\"mailto:Communilink2013@gmail.com\">Communilink2012@gmail.com</a>','FAQ','','publish','open','open','','faq-3','','','2013-02-06 17:31:15','2013-02-06 17:31:15','',0,'http://communilinkchicago.org/?page_id=201',0,'page','',0),(170,15,'2013-01-07 13:42:44','2013-01-07 13:42:44','','Frequently Asked Questions','','publish','open','open','','frequently-asked-questions-2','','','2013-01-07 13:45:50','2013-01-07 13:45:50','',0,'http://communilinkchicago.org/?page_id=170',0,'page','',0),(171,15,'2013-01-07 13:30:35','2013-01-07 13:30:35','','Frequently Asked Questions','','inherit','open','open','','170-revision','','','2013-01-07 13:30:35','2013-01-07 13:30:35','',170,'http://communilinkchicago.org/archives/171',0,'revision','',0),(173,15,'2013-01-07 13:35:14','2013-01-07 13:35:14','klajdsflkajsdf','Frequently Asked Questions','','publish','open','open','','frequently-asked-questions','','','2013-01-07 13:35:25','2013-01-07 13:35:25','',0,'http://communilinkchicago.org/?p=173',0,'post','',0),(174,15,'2013-01-07 13:32:29','2013-01-07 13:32:29','','Frequently Asked Questions','','inherit','open','open','','173-revision','','','2013-01-07 13:32:29','2013-01-07 13:32:29','',173,'http://communilinkchicago.org/archives/174',0,'revision','',0),(178,15,'2013-01-07 13:34:20','2013-01-07 13:34:20','kjalfdkj','','','inherit','open','open','','173-revision-3','','','2013-01-07 13:34:20','2013-01-07 13:34:20','',173,'http://communilinkchicago.org/archives/178',0,'revision','',0),(176,15,'2013-01-07 13:32:31','2013-01-07 13:32:31','kjalfdkj','Frequently Asked Questions','','inherit','open','open','','173-revision-2','','','2013-01-07 13:32:31','2013-01-07 13:32:31','',173,'http://communilinkchicag